rows.label: bf11430150_0020
rows.name: You're impressive, even without your Driver.

rows.label: bf11430150_0030
rows.name: I guess I should thank [System:Ruby rt=Marveni ]him[/System:Ruby] for that.

rows.label: bf11430150_0040
rows.name: Your Core... it's different from a normal one.

rows.label: bf11430150_0070
rows.name:
A being made by fusing human and Blade cells,
using Judicium technology.

rows.label: bf11430150_0080
rows.name:
That's why I can use my power even
when my Driver isn't close.

rows.label: bf11430150_0090
rows.name: I've never heard of a Blade like that.

rows.label: bf11430150_0120
rows.name: Yeah, I heard a rumor that you guys were in Iira.

rows.label: bf11430150_0130
rows.name:
I came looking for you,
and just happened to stumble upon this.

rows.label: bf11430150_0150
rows.name: It's been two years since I last saw him.
